title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Conzemius/Bercich/Krawczynski/Burnsy
description: Nordo is in for PA! How about them Twins? He is then joined by Justin Conzemius to talk the postponed Gopher Football season. Then it's Pete Bercich, along with a farewell to Everson Griffen as he makes his way to Dallas. The Athletic's Jon Krawczynski to deliver some words of wisdom and Gopher Illustrated's own bow master, Ryan Burns join. And finally, comedian Cy Amundson to talk about the Griffen departure.
